long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
While there are other extensions that support hundreds of stores, they often overlook many existing codes. We've chosen to focus exclusively on one store (we're big fans of AliExpress) and ensure the most comprehensive and up-to-date database of AliExpress free shipping coupons.

The process is incredibly simple: on the checkout page, you'll be notified of the number of available coupons. Just click "Check them all," and we'll automatically apply the highest discount to your shopping cart.

It's time to start saving!
